title: CC2
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 6ug total RNA (Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2001, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on Affymetrix HG U133 plus 2.0. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 400.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner  (GCS) 3000.
description: Gene expression data from Colon Tumour Sample
data_processing: The data were analyzed using a commercially available software package, Partek Genomics Suite 6.4 (Partek Incorporated, Missouri, USA), PLIER algorithm using default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method and t-test  to assess differentially expressed genes. The Strand Genomics Avadis software package (Strand Genomics Pvt Ltd, http://www.strandgenomics.com) was employed for hierarchical clustering of differentially expressed genes.
contact_institute: KING FAISAL SPECIALIST HOSPITAL & RESEARCH CENTER

scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner  (GCS) 3000.
description: Gene expression data from Normal paired Tissue
data_processing: The data were analyzed using a commercially available software package, Partek Genomics Suite 6.4 (Partek Incorporated, Missouri, USA), PLIER algorithm using default analysis settings and global scaling as normalization method and t-test  to assess differentially expressed genes. The Strand Genomics Avadis software package (Strand Genomics Pvt Ltd, http://www.strandgenomics.com) was employed for hierarchical clustering of differentially expressed genes.
